      "name": "Relative hemolysis index validation against in-vitro blood analogue experiments",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) derived from power-law hemolysis model integrated along Lagrangian particle tracks, compared against measured plasma-free haemoglobin from standardised in-vitro loop experiments using bovine blood at 37°C. Five flow-speed combinations evaluated. Relative hemolysis index RH computed as ratio to predicate device NIH.",
