    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate NIH predictions within 20% of experimental measurements across all five operating points, with RH < 1.0 satisfying the COU acceptance criterion. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
